          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Your heart’s unveiled to me."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Now I’d just like to see You gain me fully."
